item.title: CVE-2020-24551|2024-08-04T15:12:09.080Z -- iproom -- mmc%2B%20server
item.description: IProom MMC+ Server login page does not validate specific parameters properly. Attackers can use the vulnerability to redirect to any malicious site and steal the victim's login credentials.
